955
01:00:09,057 --> 01:00:12,096
And try to milk the moment.
Enough, enough, enough.

956
01:00:12,097 --> 01:00:14,736
Let me interrupt with the solution
to all this.

957
01:00:14,737 --> 01:00:17,056
Because later on in the year,
hopefully, we are

958
