01:00:23,017 --> 01:00:25,656
and the McLaren P1 down to our track

961
01:00:25,657 --> 01:00:28,456
and we will see
which is the fastest.

962
01:00:28,457 --> 01:00:30,056
Should be quite good, actually.

963
01:00:30,057 --> 01:00:31,896
Hopefully, we will be able to put
together

964
01:00:31,897 --> 01:00:33,456
June, July sometime, around then.

965
01:00:33,457 --> 01:00:35,496
And it'll basically be
England versus Germany.

966
01:00:35,497 --> 01:00:39,936
